Package: ProteoViz
Type: Package
Title: ProteoViz: Interactive Proteomics Data Analysis
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Who wrote it
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: Provides interactive Shiny dashboards and scriptable core functions
    for processing, normalising, and statistically analysing quantitative
    proteomics data from DIA (EncyclopeDIA) and Spectronaut workflows. The core
    functions can be used independently of the Shiny interface for reproducible
    scripted analyses.
